column5: Very well done! I hope you are very proud of yourself! Incredible achievement!!

I know how that feels.  It's all too much. Don't you feel like you belong on another planet? The world is hard, but never give up on yourself. You are way important to many people. Try and remove those thought from your head. Whatever happens, it wil be dealt with. We must wake up with no judgement of ourselves. Mindfulness is helpful. 
Gentle kind thoughts on yourself !!❤🌻🙏
